Interface LazyLocation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<LazyLocation>, HyperRect<LazyLocation>

    public interface LazyLocation
extends HyperRect<LazyLocation>, Comparable<LazyLocation>
    A lazy-loaded Location object. This allows for the system to keep and store Locations without needing the referenced World to be loaded.

    Michael Ziluck
